Attributes.description: Paleoecology of terrestrial ecosystems, particularly during the Quaternary, application of historical context to inform contemporary Anthropocene policy and management dilemmas, and including a foundation in relevant ecosystem and ecological concepts.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: Either (a) one of GEOB 102, GEOS 102, GEOB 200, GEOS 200, GEOB 204, GEOS 204, GEOB 207, GEOS 207, GEOG 211, BIOL 230 or (b) EOSC 340.
